info.title: SCAN
info.description:
This documentation covers the basics of the SCAN API.  
It is important to include the `Application-id` header in every request. It allows to dissociate the device/context from which the request was made.

You can get a token from your profile on the netw4ppl web application.

post.description:
This query allows the addition of a relation between 2 already stored refugees. The body must be in json format and follow the following structure:

``` json
[
  {
    "from_unique_id": "",
    "to_unique_id": "",
    "relation": "",
    "date": "",
    "detail": ""
  },
  {
    "from_unique_id": "",
    "to_unique_id": "",
    "relation": "",
    "date": "",
    "detail": ""
  }
]

```

The server may respond with an error if one of the required fields is not provided or if the data type is wrong.

example.message: The 0.from must be a valid UUID.
